kill $(cat /home/brandon/projects/Ereader/server.pid) 2>/dev/null
cd /home/brandon/projects/Ereader/backend && ./run.sh &
```

For the static web server (port 8090), check `ps aux | grep 8090` for the actual command ‚Äî varies (often `python3 -m http.server 8090 --directory web`).

